{
  "stem": "6719.9",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was a good ending of the Day of Atonement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He atoned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He should have hung himself 30 years ago, before that, or 40 years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, the next guy is the opera singer, Kuehneman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is the one that they found-- again, Rudy Vrba-- Rudy Vrba is tremendous, this guy, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He finds them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kuehneman, it's K-U-E-H-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His first name was Hans or Heinz, Hans Kuehneman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His trial was in 1991 and in 1992, because they found a new witness about an atrocity that he had committed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they had to do the trial all over again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got out of it too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He has a heart disease.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- the trial went for about two years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the last six months of the trial, he did never appear in court.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they decided-- not the court, but the High Court in Germany decided-- that they can't try anybody that is so sick that they can't appear in court.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Although, it was found that this same Kuehneman was going out Christmas shopping.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he carried parcels with a bad heart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But anyhow, he's off too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He killed a little Dutchman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we worked in Kanada, which I told you about, we carried all the fineries to the barracks where the girls were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were also a lot of blankets that they folded up and stacked up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to send stuff-- a little food to them in the blankets, with the stuff that we found in the suitcases were in the blanket, and we had brought over to the girls.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, just before me, little-- Joop, that was his name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He must have been about maybe 17, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He brings a blanket in.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
